::Prowl::

Prowl was too busy to hear Iris, watching Iron Raptor swing at 
shadow. His eyes don't shift as Shadow throws a gun at him.

Prowl feels a tingling in his wing-mounted orbs as his mind reaches 
out to strike the gun, making it fly off course and miss him.

-Duck!- he 'yells' to her over thought, projecting what he saw to 
her, which was Shadow jumping behind her and slashing at her neck.

His guns take aim, firing a few dozen laser shots at Shadow.
